#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:1
msgid "Contacts (`lu_mcp_contact`)"
msgstr "Contacts (`lu_mcp_contact`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:3
msgid "**6 tools** for Odoo `res.partner` (contacts and companies) management."
msgstr "Odoo 담당자(``res.partner``) 관리를 위한 **6가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `contacts` app (base)."
msgstr "필수: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `contacts` 앱(기본)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools let an AI client search, read, create, and update Odoo "
"contacts and companies, list sub-contacts (individuals under a company), "
"and post internal notes."
msgstr ""
"이 도구들을 통해 AI 클라이언트는 Odoo 담당자 및 회사를 검색, 읽기, 생성 및 업데이트하고, "
"하위 담당자(회사 하위 개인)를 나열하고, 내부 메모를 게시할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:16
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:18
msgid "`contact_search_contacts`"
msgstr "`contact_search_contacts`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:20
msgid "Search contacts and companies."
msgstr "담당자 및 회사를 검색합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`query`"
msgstr "`query`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Keyword search across name, email, and phone."
msgstr "이름, 이메일 및 전화번호에서 키워드 검색."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`is_company`"
msgstr "`is_company`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "boolean"
msgstr "boolean"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`true` for companies only, `false` for individuals only."
msgstr "회사만: `true`, 개인만: `false`."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`customer_rank`"
msgstr "`customer_rank`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Minimum customer rank (1 = is a customer)."
msgstr "최소 고객 등급(1 = 고객임)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`supplier_rank`"
msgstr "`supplier_rank`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Minimum supplier rank (1 = is a supplier)."
msgstr "최소 공급업체 등급(1 = 공급업체임)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Maximum results (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "최대 결과 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:30 ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:44
#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:64 ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:83
#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:96 ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:110
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:31
msgid "*\"Search for all customers named 'Kim'.\"*"
msgstr "*\"'Kim'이라는 이름의 모든 고객을 검색하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:35
msgid "`contact_read_contact`"
msgstr "`contact_read_contact`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:37
msgid ""
"Get full details of a contact or company: address, VAT, ranks, sub-"
"contacts, tags, and internal notes."
msgstr "담당자의 전체 상세 정보를 가져옵니다: 주소, VAT, 등급, 하위 담당자, 태그 및 내부 메모."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`id`"
msgstr "`id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Partner ID."
msgstr "파트너 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:45
msgid "*\"Show me full details for contact #42.\"*"
msgstr "*\"담당자 #42의 전체 상세 정보를 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:49
msgid "`contact_create_contact`"
msgstr "`contact_create_contact`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:51
msgid "Create a new contact or company."
msgstr "새 담당자 또는 회사를 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`name`"
msgstr "`name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Contact or company name."
msgstr "담당자 또는 회사 이름."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`true` to create a company, `false` for an individual."
msgstr "회사 생성: `true`, 개인 생성: `false`."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`parent_id`"
msgstr "`parent_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Parent company ID (creates the contact under a company)."
msgstr "모회사 ID(담당자를 회사 아래 생성합니다)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`email`"
msgstr "`email`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Email address."
msgstr "이메일 주소."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`phone`"
msgstr "`phone`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Phone number."
msgstr "전화번호."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`street`"
msgstr "`street`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Street address."
msgstr "도로명 주소."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`city`"
msgstr "`city`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "City."
msgstr "도시."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`country_id`"
msgstr "`country_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Country ID (Odoo `res.country` ID)."
msgstr "국가 ID(Odoo `res.country` ID)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:65
msgid ""
"*\"Create a company contact named 'Seoul Tech Co.' with email "
"info@seoultech.kr.\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"'Seoul Tech Co.'라는 이름의 회사 담당자를 생성하고 이메일을 info@seoultech.kr로 설정하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:69
msgid "`contact_update_contact`"
msgstr "`contact_update_contact`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:71
msgid "Update an existing contact or company."
msgstr "기존 담당자를 업데이트합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New name."
msgstr "새 이름."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New email."
msgstr "새 이메일."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New phone number."
msgstr "새 전화번호."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New street address."
msgstr "새 도로명 주소."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New city."
msgstr "새 도시."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "New country ID."
msgstr "새 국가 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:84
msgid "*\"Update contact #42 — set email to new@example.com and city to Busan.\"*"
msgstr "*\"담당자 #42 업데이트 — 이메일을 new@example.com으로, 도시를 Busan으로 설정.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:88
msgid "`contact_list_children`"
msgstr "`contact_list_children`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:90
msgid "List individual contacts (employees, contacts) under a company."
msgstr "회사 파트너의 직접 하위 담당자를 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Company partner ID."
msgstr "회사 파트너 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:97
msgid "*\"List all contacts under company #10 (Acme Corp).\"*"
msgstr "*\"회사 #10(Acme Corp) 아래의 모든 담당자를 나열하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:101
msgid "`contact_log_note`"
msgstr "`contact_log_note`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:103
msgid "Post an internal note on a contact record (not visible externally)."
msgstr "담당자 레코드에 내부 메모를 게시합니다(외부에 표시되지 않음)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "`body`"
msgstr "`body`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md
msgid "Note body (Markdown)."
msgstr "메모 본문(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/contact.md:111
msgid ""
"*\"Log a note on contact #42: 'Spoke at KCD 2026 — interested in "
"enterprise plan.'\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"담당자 #42에 메모 기록: 'KCD 2026에서 발표함 — 엔터프라이즈 플랜에 관심 있음.'\"*"

